paragraphs:
[18]
Section 77 of the
Act
provides that the Governor-in-Council may make regulations, among other things, for:
(
d
) prescribing a fee for the purpose of paragraph 11(1)(a) and the manner of calculating fees or amounts payable for the purposes of paragraphs 11(1)(b) and (c) and subsections 11(2) and (3);
d) fixer le montant des droits prévus à l'alinéa 11(1)a) et déterminer le mode de calcul du montant exigible en vertu des alinéas 11(1)b) et c) et des paragraphes 11(2) et (3);
